OL,4,CPay rise for Aldi lorry drivers amid
OL,5,Cshortage
OL,6, Aldi has increased its wages for lorry
OL,7, drivers amid a chronic shortage of
OL,8, drivers across the industry.
OL,10,FThe supermarket chain confirmed the
OL,11,Frise following similar incentives by
OL,12,Fgrocers to attract HGV drivers.
OL,14,FThe lack of drivers has caused
OL,15,Fdisruption and delays in various supply
OL,16,Fchains, which has led to product
OL,17,Fshortages in some industries.
OL,19,FTesco has offered drivers a #1,000
OL,20,Fjoining bonus for candidates who join
OL,21,Fbefore 30 September.
